{"data":[{"name":"20:25","price":"അദ്ദേഹം പറഞ്ഞു: എന്‍റെ രക്ഷിതാവേ, നീ എനിക്ക് ഹൃദയവിശാലത നല്‍കേണമേ.","arabic":"قَالَ رَبِّ ٱشۡرَحۡ لِي صَدۡرِي","category":["20 (Ta-Ha)","Ta-Ha","Surah Ta-Ha"],"ayahNumber":2373,"juzNumber":16,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"qāla rabbi ish'raḥ lī ṣadrī ","translations":["He said","My Lord","Expand","for me","my breast","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["qāla","rabbi","ish'raḥ","lī","ṣadrī",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,760],[2,760,1440],[3,1440,2070],[4,2070,2470],[5,2470,3805]]}},{"name":"20:26","price":"എനിക്ക് എന്‍റെ കാര്യം നീ എളുപ്പമാക്കിത്തരേണമേ.","arabic":"وَيَسِّرۡ لِيٓ أَمۡرِي","category":["20 (Ta-Ha)","Ta-Ha","Surah Ta-Ha"],"ayahNumber":2374,"juzNumber":16,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wayassir lī amrī ","translations":["And ease","for me","my task","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["wayassir","lī","amrī",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,3050],[3,3050,4365]]}},{"name":"20:27","price":"എന്‍റെ നാവില്‍ നിന്ന് നീ കെട്ടഴിച്ചുതരേണമേ.(5)","arabic":"وَٱحۡلُلۡ عُقۡدَةٗ مِّن لِّسَانِي","category":["20 (Ta-Ha)","Ta-Ha","Surah Ta-Ha"],"ayahNumber":2375,"juzNumber":16,"footnotes":"5) മൂസാ നബി(عليه السلام)ക്ക് വിക്ക് ഉണ്ടായിരുന്നു. അത് ഒഴിവായി കിട്ടുവാന്‍ വേണ്ടിയാണ് അദ്ദേഹം പ്രാര്‍ഥിച്ചത്.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-uḥ'lul ʿuq'datan min lisānī ","translations":["And untie","(the) knot","from","my tongue","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-uḥ'lul","ʿuq'datan","min","lisānī",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,1870],[3,1870,2980],[4,2980,4655]]}},{"name":"20:28","price":"ജനങ്ങള്‍ എന്‍റെ സംസാരം മനസ്സിലാക്കേണ്ടതിന്‌.","arabic":"يَفۡقَهُواْ قَوۡلِي","category":["20 (Ta-Ha)","Ta-Ha","Surah Ta-Ha"],"ayahNumber":2376,"juzNumber":16,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"yafqahū qawlī ","translations":["That they may understand","my speech","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["yafqahū","qawlī",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,2525]]}}],"dua":{"id":21,"name":"Dua for Mental C